title: Dogs or Cats?
contents: surprise, it's turtles, you stupid moron idiots. you thought that dogs were somehow above it all? that cats were actually superior in any way to turtles? i'm not talking tortoises, those jokes can suck eggs, turtles are where its at. they'll outlive us all. just you wait.
